{
  "id": 6411735804674048,
  "name": "Web Smart Card API",
  "summary": "Enables smart card (PC/SC) applications to move to the Web platform. It gives them access to the PC/SC implementation (and card reader drivers) available in the host OS.\n\nAdministrators can control the availability of this API either:\n- Globally—using the DefaultSmartCardConnectSetting policy.\n- Per-application—using the SmartCardConnectAllowedForUrls and SmartCardConnectBlockedForUrls policies.",
